Zen_Bob_Sadie_Nate: “Congratulations, Player_ch! You made it this far, and we're so proud of the journey you've been on. You've grown so much. But now you have a choice to make\: stay with us or return to your old world. Know that we'll support whichever choice you make, and you'll always have a place with us.”

Player_ch: “Thank you, guys.”

Zen_Bob_Sadie_Nate: “If you choose your old home, you'll get your suit back. But if you choose to stay here, our world will give you clothes that reflect your true identity.”